'''奥高‧勃佐尔格清真寺'''（{{lang-fa|مسجد آقا بزرگ}} ''Masjed-e Āghā Bozorg'')是伊朗[[伊斯法罕省|伊斯法罕省]][[卡尚|卡尚]]的一座历史悠久的清真寺。该清真寺由Ustad Haj Sa'ban-ali建于18世纪。该清真寺和经学院位于城市中心。

奥高‧勃佐尔格清真寺被誉为“卡尚最好的伊斯兰建筑群，以及19世纪中叶最好的伊斯兰建筑群之一”。<ref name="Burke2010">{{cite book|last=Burke|first=Andrew|title=Iran|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=gEca_4iSNCUC&pg=PA228|date=15 September 2010|publisher=Lonely Planet|isbn=978-1-74220-349-2|page=228|access-date=2016-01-30|archive-date=2021-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305183153/https://books.google.com/books?id=gEca_4iSNCUC&pg=PA228|dead-url=no}}</ref> 它以对称设计著称<ref name="PlanetBurke2012">{{cite book|last1=Burke|first1=Andrew|last2=Maxwell|first2=Virginia|first3=Iain|last3=Shearer|title=Lonely Planet Iran|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=TY0GUQjhDX0C&pg=PT366|date=1 June 2012|publisher=Lonely Planet|isbn=978-1-74321-320-9|page=366|access-date=2016-01-30|archive-date=2020-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200830154926/https://books.google.com/books?id=TY0GUQjhDX0C&pg=PT366|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

